{"tid":2132541,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 美國公布第 2 季度 GDP 初值 :   (- 32.9%)  好過市場預期 !!!","createTime":"2020-07-30T12:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T17:56:22.000Z","uid":29093,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"accbfba7fe98e8d5b177bbfff46ab09dcd3f8e46","tid":2132541,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"上季終值 : - 5.0%<br />\n預期值 :  - 34.1%<br />\n<br />\n初值 : - 32.9% <br />\n<br />\n重磅指數:  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c30b1e7c8fb4aed13e5fbb81dbaceb4a68d270","tid":2132541,"uid":146285,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"美國公佈既GDP叫「環比年化增速」，唔係香港同中國計既&rsquo;同比&rsquo;year-on-year, &lsquo;環比&rsquo;quarter-on-quarter<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大體含義是：將2020年第一季度的GDP，與2019年的GDP做對比後，再轉換成年率。舉個例子，假如2019年第四季度的GDP是100，到2020年第一季度的GDP是101，這環比增長了1%。然後再假設未來三個季度的GDP環比增速都是1%，這樣就可以得出一整年的「環比年化增速略微超過4%」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/finance/a6nmakx.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Ffinance%2Fa6nmakx.html&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=78ee97f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/finance/a6nmakx.html</a>"},{"pid":"58e0a876895aeb0bc885a045074ca12bd4f02fae","tid":2132541,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"d1ad66703c146758a3c0256c0c6349b972612b59","tid":2132541,"uid":299433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma