class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed0dac63b5fc4589fea2ce409b2890a5d856c98","tid":2132541,"uid":157525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"2季度負值已經confirm經濟衰退"},{"pid":"bcd1dd7aee93a7049363fc2909a3ad142c3ce3cd","tid":2132541,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"環乜撚比<br />\n<br />\n支國落黎既？"},{"pid":"4b5536761e7544c0556c60aeb0e1f00366cbccde","tid":2132541,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"【全球攬炒】美國第2季經濟勁縮32.9% 二戰後有統計以來最傷<br />\n <br />\n2020年07月30日(四) 20:33 <br />\n<br />\n美國商務部周四(30日)公布，當地第2季國內生產總值（GDP）以年率計勁縮32.9%，為二戰後有統計以來最傷，較首季的5%跌幅顯著擴大，但略好過經濟學家估計的34.5%跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n美國上季經濟嚴重收縮，反映為阻止新冠肺炎疫症蔓延，美國各地早前實施封鎖和社交距離等措施，但此舉令經濟活動陷入停擺。當中，佔美國經濟比重約2/3的個人消費，第2季亦慘跌34.6%，稍差過預期跌34.5%。<br />\n<br />\n儘管美國經濟已逐步重啟，但鑑於疫情最近再呈惡化，美國復甦前景依然極不明朗。"},{"pid":"19d28ccd465facb991acc77196bf1bc60c2ece26","tid":2132541,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"支那廢炎累撚到美國創二戰後既最大經濟衰退 <br />\n<br />\n第三次世界大戰已靜靜埋下伏線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8ecc7eb7c688f30abe881ea8129cf212f50782","tid":2132541,"uid":33392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"price in左，所以升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a778fa50ba9391407d7404d2f61b294d1b4c184","tid":2132541,"uid":273439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">好過預期.........................<br />\n個預期特登高估咁多...................</span></span>"},{"pid":"5afdbf69a91bc4d306453